<h1 id="simpler-sidebar">simpler-sidebar</h1>
<p><a href="https://gitter.im/dcdeiv/simpler-sidebar?utm_source=badge&amp;utm_medium=badge&amp;utm_campaign=pr-badge&amp;utm_content=badge"><img alt="Join the chat at https://gitter.im/dcdeiv/simpler-sidebar" src="https://badges.gitter.im/dcdeiv/simpler-sidebar.svg" /></a>
<a href="https://badge.fury.io/gh/dcdeiv%2Fsimpler-sidebar"><img alt="GitHub version" src="https://badge.fury.io/gh/dcdeiv%2Fsimpler-sidebar.svg" /></a>
<a href="https://badge.fury.io/bo/simpler-sidebar"><img alt="Bower version" src="https://badge.fury.io/bo/simpler-sidebar.svg" /></a>
<a href="https://badge.fury.io/js/simpler-sidebar"><img alt="npm version" src="https://badge.fury.io/js/simpler-sidebar.svg" /></a>
<a href="#license"><img alt="MIT and GPL-2 license" src="https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT%20and%20GPL--2.0-blue.svg" /></a>
<a href="https://travis-ci.org/dcdeiv/simpler-sidebar"><img alt="Build Status" src="https://travis-ci.org/dcdeiv/simpler-sidebar.svg?branch=master" /></a></p>

<p>A jQuery plugin that allows to <em>create a side nav</em> as in modern mobile apps. It aims to <em>simplicity</em> so that <em>everybody can use it</em> no matter if expert programmers or not.</p>

<p><strong>simpler-sidebar</strong> is a fork of <a href="https://github.com/dcdeiv/simple-sidebar"><em>simple-sidebar</em></a>.</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="#download">Download</a></li>
