    <ul>
      <li>Add Grunt. Simpler-Sidebar files are moved to <code>dist/</code> and renamed to <em>jquery.simpler-sidebar.js</em> and <em>jquery.simpler-sidebar.min.js</em>.</li>
      <li>Fix <em>sidebar.closingLinks</em> and <em>sidebar.align</em>.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
